name: •  Breackable and Amazing Mountan of Dreams  •
description:
(p.1)
The light, always white but not now, I was watching the light of the soul and its inverted, the dark its broken and it spreads a white bright, and the lights are black, but, anyways the black feels so good...

It's comfortable in this black light, I don't want to see the white darkness, it looks so sad, like there's no one alive to tell me what's going on in there or whatever...

I miss the white, but now I'm okay with the dark...
